extends ../generate/layout/_layout

block title
  - var title = "News: Traffic Arbitrage, Marketing, Digital"

block content
  main.main
    +banner({
      image: 'https://palai.media/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1920x540_desktop-1.png'
    }).banner--wide

    section.section
      .container-fluid
        .container
          +breadcrumbs([
            {
              text: 'Main page',
              url: './'
            },
            {
              text: 'News',
              url: null
            }
          ])

          .content.content--left
            .content__header
              h1.content__title= title
              .text.content__text
                p Fresh news from the world of affiliate marketing, crypto, and online business. Updates from advertising platforms, new releases, and the latest developments in the digital space. A quick overview of what matters most.
            .content__left
              +filters.js-filters
            .content__center
              .grid
                each item, index in ARTICLES
                  .col-12.col-mob-m-6.col-desk-s-4
                    +article-alt(item).article--alt
                .col-12
                  +pagination
            .content__right
              +banner({
                image: 'https://palai.media/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/768h540-1.png'
              })

    section.section
      .container-fluid
        .container
          +banner({
            image: 'https://palai.media/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1920x540_desktop-1.png'
          })

    section.section
      .container-fluid
        .container
          .text
            h3 Affiliate Program Ranking by “Heaffen” Media
            br
            p There are many CPA affiliate networks — several thousand — and their number continues to grow.
            br
            p Our team has prepared a list of top CPA networks, including affiliate programs from different verticals. The editorial team at “Heaffen” Media keeps a close eye on the market and works to update the affiliate program ranking as quickly as possible. So if you don’t find the one you need yet, feel free to contact us at admin@heaffen.media or on Telegram @heaffen_sales.
            br
            p Before starting to work with any CPA affiliate network from the list, we recommend reviewing information about the program, checking the company’s social media, and reading reviews. Remember, when choosing an affiliate network to run traffic, you are choosing a partner with whom you will earn money. So don’t neglect basic checks to ensure the company’s reliability and safety.
            br
            p Choose your top CPA network or affiliate program and start driving traffic with a cosmic ROI! 🚀
